org.apache.taverna.server.master.usage

Class UsageRecordRecorder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.server.master.utils.JDOSupport<UsageRecord>
      • org.apache.taverna.server.master.usage.UsageRecordRecorder

  • public class UsageRecordRecorder
extends JDOSupport<UsageRecord>
    A simple state-aware writer of usage records. It just appends them, one by one, to the file whose name is stored in the state.
    Author:
    Donal Fellows
